    "description": "<strong>在这个充满扭曲幽默感的惩罚性3D平台游戏中，骑着卖热狗的大虾穿越一个超现实而危险的岛屿。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><br><strong>醒来，战士！</strong><br>你扮演着“甲壳动物行动”的唯一幸存者，被困在一个秘密的世界里。探索一个充满危险的黑暗岛屿，揭开它的神秘面纱，寻找回家的路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/85d4699921b225d51275f0719b75b3f5.poster.avif?t=1715021156\" width=384 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/85d4699921b225d51275f0719b75b3f5.webm?t=1715021156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/85d4699921b225d51275f0719b75b3f5.mp4?t=1715021156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br>挑战独特的骑虾控制和游戏的永久死亡机制，需要发挥出你所有的技巧。<br>按下按钮可以即时在两种控制方案之间切换：“精准”以获取准确的控制和直接的垂直移动；“疾驰”则可以快速前进，但需要提前规划，因为其增加的动力需要更多的计划。<br>避开致命的陷阱，遇到荒谬的敌人，面对将推你极限的史诗级首领。<br>体验一个超现实和扭曲的幽默感，会让你同时发笑和颤抖。<br>发现稀有的永久性强化道具，让你在这个具有挑战性的冒险中占据优势。<br><br><strong>你有勇气在这个奇异的岛屿上生存并逃脱吗？上吧！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/82c4b294dae0ffa292ddaff935a66d66.poster.avif?t=1715021156\" width=384 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/82c4b294dae0ffa292ddaff935a66d66.webm?t=1715021156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/82c4b294dae0ffa292ddaff935a66d66.mp4?t=1715021156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亮点</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 尽显独立游戏的风范-由独立开发者设计和制作<br></li><li> 具有扭曲幽默感的黑暗而氛围的世界<br></li><li> 硬核3D平台游戏，具有独特的基于物理的控制<br></li><li> 永久死亡功能，少量检查点，带来挑战性的体验<br></li><li> 稀有而珍贵的永久性强化道具需要发现和收集<br></li><li> 荒谬的敌人等待遭遇和打败<br></li><li> 史诗级的首领拥有独特的机制和困难的挑战</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/6e6ff93f4a7edf8a9234a47e6159462c.poster.avif?t=1715021156\" width=384 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/6e6ff93f4a7edf8a9234a47e6159462c.webm?t=1715021156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338300/extras/6e6ff93f4a7edf8a9234a47e6159462c.mp4?t=1715021156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
